        "content": "\u003cdiv class=\"netsage-banner\"\u003e\n  \u003ctable class=\"netsage-nav\" style=\"width: 100%; border: none;\"\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFile Transfer Data:\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\n        \u003cul\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/efsbhqrc8iqrke?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top sources/destinations of file transfers?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/ffsoxhu8ceolca?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the top transfers by organization?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/dfsbhtkemmebkc?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat do individual transfers between sites look like?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli\u003e\u003ca class=\"netsage-button-q\" href=\"/d/bfsbho9ta15hcb?from=${__from}\u0026to=${__to}\"\u003eWhat are the file transfer data summary statistics?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\n      \u003c/td\u003e\n      \n  \u003c/table\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"netsage-column\"\u003e\n\n    \n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cstyle\u003e\n  .netsage-banner {\n  background-color: #618ED0;\n  padding: 1rem 15rem;\n  }\n  a.netsage-button-q {\n  color: white;\n  background-color: #759FDD;\n  padding: 4px;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  }\n  a.netsage-button-q:hover {\n  color: white;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav tr, .netsage-nav td, .netsage-nav th{\n  border: none !important;\n  background: none !important;\n  color: white;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav td {\n  vertical-align: top;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav th h2{\n  font-weight: 800;\n  }\n  .netsage-nav li {\n  margin-top: 4px;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n  font-size: 14pt;\n  }\n\u003c/style\u003e",
